":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6c4649f60b8731963afb357aa2cb40a6a38bd16","tid":2354262,"uid":7369,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"7240c75b44d5d1b245bf00685af281f77e5097ac","tid":2354262,"uid":66087,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"冇記錯 Tesla 支那版大部份零件係國產，電池係寧德時代，其實即係內循環成功左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T10:49:58.000Z","msg":"即係貼牌Tesla?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T10:52:22.000Z","msg":"出個system<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5738b251ceccb211d4e7bfe34eb65c5fcf2966dd","tid":2354262,"uid":293225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7240c75b44d5d1b245bf00685af281f77e5097ac","tid":2354262,"uid":66087,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"冇記錯 Tesla 支那版大部份零件係國產，電池係寧德時代，其實即係內循環成功左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"鋰礦無得內循環。<br />\n其實電池毛利好低安全要求又高，只有出貨量夠大先有少少錢賺。<br />\n如果鋰礦原料斷供中國，呢啲靠借錢維持嘅公司即死。"},{"pid":"2fff547ad41c0ebbe5f8d5e4041522116f42c6a9","tid":2354262,"uid":66087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20191106/NVTRSFIPKX46XCFGWAELPQNWAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20191106%2FNVTRSFIPKX46XCFGWAELPQNWAE%2F&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=b2d8e76f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20191106%2FNVTRSFIPKX46XCFGWAELPQNWAE%2F&h=ffba8d13\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20191106/NVTRSFIPKX46XCFGWAELPQNWAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n更新時間： 2019/11/06 11:33<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》引述消息人士說法報導，美國電動車廠特斯拉（TESLA）和中國電池廠寧德時代（CATL）已達成初步協議，最快將從明年開始採用寧德時代供應的電